description: Number of symmetrical planar partitions of n: planar partitions (A000219) that when regarded as 3-D objects have a threefold axis of symmetry that is the intersection of 3 mirror planes, i.e. C3v symmetry.
links: Wouter Meeussen, Table of n, a(n) for n=1..151
example: The plane partition {{2,1},{1}} has C3v symmetry.
author: _Wouter Meeussen_
